<h2>How to Play .flv Files</h2>
<p>To play an.flv file on Windows or Mac OS you'll need a media player that is compatible with these files. FLV players include VLC and Winamp, along with other well-known media players. If you don't have a media player installed on your computer that works for playing Flash Videos, you can use our .flv converter to change the file to a different format.</p>
